    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new professional development module for our senior leadership team. Can you give me some general tips on how employees should handle their grooming and overall appearance to make sure they're projecting maximum authority and professionalism when they're in high-level boardroom meetings?",
