      "content": "For high-level meetings, a sharp, conservative look is key to projecting authority. Men should opt for well-tailored suits in dark, classic colors, ensuring their grooming is immaculate—neat hair and clean-shaven or a meticulously trimmed beard. Women should favor tailored business attire, like pant suits or elegant dresses, with minimal, sophisticated makeup and polished hair. The overall message should be one of unwavering control and impeccable presentation.",
