    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I've had some questions come up from a few different departments about specific styles. For example, some of our more diverse staff have asked about how things like natural hair textures or cultural accessories might be perceived in those high-stakes environments. How should they balance staying true to their identity while still meeting that standard of 'impeccable presentation' you mentioned?",
